<span id="freeTextContainer5430503439994835431">Louise Penny rocks! This is excellent! She brings out the French in my heritage, a trilingual immersion graduate as a child. I picture the whole French flavour in the names, sounds, and place. And she does the Canadian wilderness proud, making me want blueberries, chocolate, and cheese very acutely. You don&apos;t just get a mystery from this master auteure: you travel along on a complete cultural experience. First edition hardcover, review to come, mes belles amies!</span>
