<div id="review_2764806581" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2764806581" />
    <a title="Brenda" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/2337007-brenda"><img alt="Brenda" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1640947679p2/2337007.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2764806581?book_show_action=true">May 14, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Brenda" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Brenda" href="/user/show/2337007-brenda">Brenda</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9781250031129" href="/book/show/16045144-the-beautiful-mystery">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2337007-brenda?shelf=2013-release">2013-release</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2337007-brenda?shelf=crime">crime</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2337007-brenda?shelf=borrowed-from-library">borrowed-from-library</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2337007-brenda?shelf=canadian-author">canadian-author</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2337007-brenda?shelf=mystery">mystery</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2764806581" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8971907616382669341">In <i>The Beautiful Mystery</i>, 8th in the Chief Inspector Armand Gamache series by Louise Penny, we are taken to the monastery of Saint-Gilbert-Entre-les-Loups, located on the edge of a lake in the isolated lands of Quebec, where no others – except the monks – had ever been allowed admittance. Twenty four monks living in the peace and tranquility the order had known for centuries. Now, their peace had been shattered – there were twenty three after their choir director was murdered. It was up to Gamac</span>
  <span id="freeText8971907616382669341" style="display:none">In <i>The Beautiful Mystery</i>, 8th in the Chief Inspector Armand Gamache series by Louise Penny, we are taken to the monastery of Saint-Gilbert-Entre-les-Loups, located on the edge of a lake in the isolated lands of Quebec, where no others – except the monks – had ever been allowed admittance. Twenty four monks living in the peace and tranquility the order had known for centuries. Now, their peace had been shattered – there were twenty three after their choir director was murdered. It was up to Gamache and his second in charge Jean Guy Beauvoir to find the murderer.<br /><br />But there was tension amid the peace; the only time everyone came together as one was when they joined in the singing, in the chanting. It was beautiful to Gamache. He knew also that there were secrets he needed to discover. Could he? But before the murderer was found, there would be horror unearthed. Would they survive it?<br /><br />Set in a completely different location to the usual of Three Pines, nevertheless I thoroughly enjoyed this one. Fascinating, grueling, frustrating – I’ll have to get on to the next very soon after that ending! Highly recommended.</span>
  <a data-text-id="8971907616382669341" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
